snippet.title: TRex Hero Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://bit.ly/TRexHeroSteamPage

Protect the dinosaur eggs from an asteroid rain and save the world in TRex Hero. TRex Hero is a hilarious action game where you will have to literally run from one side to the other of the screen to save your life, while rescuing future generations of dinosaurs. Avoid the funny effects caused by asteroids, like freezing you, burning your tail, electrocuting you, or even making you throw up, while taking advantage of power-ups like your pterodactyl shield buddy, your powerful dash, and more!
